# 8.3 Tavily MCP

---

## Purpose

The Tavily MCP server provides access to live web search.

Unlike Gemini's internal knowledge, Tavily retrieves current information from the internet.

Examples include:

- University Rankings
- Official Websites
- Latest Course Information
- Recent University Updates
- Tuition Information

---

## Why Tavily?

A language model has a knowledge cutoff.

University rankings and admissions change every year.

Therefore,

real-time web search is required.

Tavily fills this gap.

---

## Communication Type

```
Remote MCP

↓

Streamable HTTP
```

Connection

```python
StreamableHTTPConnectionParams(
    url=f"https://mcp.tavily.com/mcp/?tavilyApiKey={TAVILY_API_KEY}"
)
```

---

## Responsibilities

Tavily answers questions such as

```
Top AI universities in Germany

Best ML universities in USA

Top Computer Science universities

Official university websites

Recent ranking information
```

---

## Internal Request Flow

```
Gemini

↓

Google ADK

↓

Tavily MCP

↓

Tavily Search API

↓

Search Results

↓

Gemini
```

---

## Advantages

✓ Live data

✓ Search grounding

✓ Current rankings

✓ Reliable sources

✓ Easy integration

---

## Limitations

Cannot provide

- Weather

- Scholarships

- Visa Information

- Report Generation

---

# 8.4 Google Maps MCP

---

## Purpose

Provides geographic intelligence.

Capabilities include

- Current Weather

- Nearby Attractions

- Geocoding

- Place Information

- Directions

- Distance

---

## Why Maps?

A university recommendation is more useful when students understand the surrounding environment.

Examples

"What is the weather in Munich?"

"What attractions are near TUM?"

"How far is the airport?"

---

## Communication

```
Remote MCP

↓

Streamable HTTP
```

Configuration

```python
StreamableHTTPConnectionParams(
    url="https://mapstools.googleapis.com/mcp"
)
```

---

## Authentication

Requires

```
GOOGLE_MAPS_API_KEY
```

Unlike Tavily,

Maps requires API authentication.

---

## Responsibilities

Maps provides

Current Weather

↓

Nearby Attractions

↓

Location Information

↓

Campus Context

---

## Internal Flow

```
Gemini

↓

Google ADK

↓

Maps MCP

↓

Google Maps Service

↓

Results

↓

Gemini
```

---

## Advantages

✓ Real-time

✓ Accurate

✓ Rich geographical context

✓ Official Google Maps ecosystem

---

## Limitations

Cannot answer

- Scholarships

- University Rankings

- Visa Requirements

---

## Debugging Experience

During deployment,

Maps MCP initially failed because

Google Cloud authentication differs between

API Keys

and

Application Default Credentials (ADC).

Understanding this distinction was one of the major learnings from the project.

