# 8.5 Scholarship MCP

---

## Purpose

The Scholarship MCP is a custom-built Local MCP server.

Unlike the other MCP servers,

this server was developed specifically for the Study Abroad Finder.

---

## Why build a custom MCP?

Scholarships

Visa

Cost of Living

were project-specific requirements.

Instead of relying on another cloud service,

a local MCP server was implemented.

---

## Communication

```
Local MCP

↓

STDIO
```

Configuration

```python
StdioConnectionParams(
    server_params=...
)
```

---

## Responsibilities

The Scholarship MCP provides

Scholarships

↓

Visa Information

↓

Cost of Living

↓

Monthly Expenses

↓

Living Estimates

---

## Internal Flow

```
Gemini

↓

Google ADK

↓

STDIO

↓

Scholarship MCP

↓

Python Process

↓

Results

↓

Gemini
```

---

## Advantages

✓ Fully customizable

✓ Offline capable

✓ Runs locally

✓ Easy debugging

✓ Fast execution

