# 8.9 Final Architecture

The final MCP architecture for the Study Abroad Finder is shown below.

```
                           Gemini 2.5 Flash

                                   │

                                   ▼

                             Google ADK

        ┌──────────────────────────┼──────────────────────────┐

        ▼                          ▼                          ▼

   Tavily MCP               Google Maps MCP          Scholarship MCP

                                                          │

                                                          ▼

                                                   Filesystem MCP

                                                          │

                                                          ▼

                                                Markdown Report

                                                          │

                                                          ▼

                                                  Final Response
```

Each MCP server contributes a specialized capability, while Google ADK orchestrates their interaction and Gemini provides the reasoning that determines **which tools to use, when to use them, and how to combine their outputs**.

This modular architecture demonstrates how modern AI systems can move beyond standalone language models by integrating specialized execution services through a common protocol.

